entries.name: Maven's key chain
entries.properties:
(1) key opens his own bed chambers.(2) opens the guest bedroom.
(3) key opens the wine cellar.

100 lbs cornmeal, 2 axes sharpened, 5 lbs saltlick, 5 lbs sugar cubes, standard medicinal supplies, 0.5 lbs Tarleaf!
